ên Hưng trấn phú - 天興鎮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%C3%A1-Th%C3%B4ng/author-UlfffDmWp64stOugtjh9rQ">Nguyễn Bá Thông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/Thi%C3%AAn-thu-gi%C3%A1m-ph%C3%BA/poem-aNFJrxFI6pAICUyX7CKLvQ">Thiên thu giám phú - 千秋鑑賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-T%C3%B4ng-M%E1%BA%A1i/author-EY3eHTvDpkwLbISMoUQtYg">Phạm Tông Mại</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-B%C3%B9i-ng%C5%A9-ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Xuy%C3%AAn/poem-lOk7uSNl_EQZY5BBCOSk_g">Tống Bùi ngũ phó Đông Xuyên - 送裴五赴東川</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-t%C3%BA-t%C3%A0i-s%E1%BB%9F-c%C6%B0-song-c%E1%BB%91i-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-MfaPjs90pU41YPS6VNsznQ">Vương Phục tú tài sở cư song cối nhị thủ kỳ 1 - 王復秀才所居雙檜二首其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
